            "productSelection": "refill-booster-packs",
            "open": "open",
            "DescriptionHeading": "Overview",
            "description": "A pack of 3 x 20ml eco-concentrate refills to top up your Counter Clean Bottle for Life. Subscribe to save 15% and never run out again! \n<p> </p>\nPour an entire 20ml concentrate into your Bottle for Life and top up with ordinary tap water to make up a 300ml naturally-scented, multisurface cleaner. Spray onto surfaces or directly onto your cloth and wipe clean."
