            "productSelection": "refill-booster-packs",
            "open": "close",
            "DescriptionHeading": "Scent Information",
            "description": "Uplifting Citrus: A characterful blend of Sweet Orange, Grapefruit &amp; Naouli that's easy to love with a refreshing, juicy scent and cheerful, mood-enhancing properties.\n<p> </p>\nBalancing Floral: A beautifully floral blend of Rose Geranium, Lemon Peel and Vetiver Roots, known for their comforting &amp; balancing properties\n<p> </p>\nGrounding Vetiver: A complex and invigorating scent with an earthy blend of Sweet Orange, Coriander Seed and Vetiver, known for their calming &amp; grounding effects.\n<p> </p>\nPatchouli &amp; Cedarwood: A forest-walk blend of earthy Cedarwood with wafts of woody-citrus MayChang and Patchouli, followed by floral Palmarosa and sweet-balsamic Amyris.\n<p> </p>\nLemon &amp; MarjoramA vibrant citrussy blend, softened by grassy palmarosa, sweet marjoram and soft clary sage, for cheerful thoughts of Spring in every room."
          }
        },
